美國股票或指數ETF不再符合絕對優質的定義才止損賣出<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 以上方法無需因股價上升而止賺，除非買入的美國股票或指數ETF不再符合絕對優質的定義才止賺賣出，有非常可觀的回報，或更好的投資才考慮賣出<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 以上方法知易行難，能保持耐心和信念實行的，方能做到長久勝算高並且回報大，恭喜你已經獲得股票必勝法！"},{"pid":"5708c557888133d163b7923876e5423f5ec7b8c9","tid":2076120,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df0beb5be377b9a9afbdecbb9f38135dc1cf6ef","tid":2076120,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f556afefdeca34ff8e541e7fed4ea2b396865075","tid":2076120,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"炒左都十年,今日靜靜地無野做,埋下條數<br />\n呢十年加埋都輸左40萬<br />\n而我只係一個搵5萬既打工仔<br />\n<br />\n望返轉頭好似好on9,由第一日投資就同自己講,想搵多d,搵多幾千幫補下就夠<br />\n賺又早放,遲放又輸,呢十年好似白過咁<br />\n好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"有冇樓呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"呢個唔討論啦"},{"pid":"b2f8eee42e118042478d89b5bf637e8ff3d58fdc","tid":2076120,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5106c4bd5c652c02ebfb4654aa32a15b898783bc","tid":2076120,"uid":83910,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"認真過去五年玩牛熊輸廿萬<br />\n<br />\n最近一年戒牛熊戒港股<br />\n轉玩美股正股<br />\n<br />\n就算經歷今年三月武肺股災<br />\n都已經追返哂果廿萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬴錢既人我見唔少,不過唔係我"},{"pid":"3923b6f7bb76d1dcee51c0149ec3e3a07e1ea4ba","tid":2076120,"uid":40309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258bab08d8c61abae5c7714d14fa569f27bfc079","tid":2076120,"uid":186431,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"搵兩萬，5年輸60萬<img src=